Package: defvalues
Title: An R package to easily deflate monetary values
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Fabricio", "Ferreira", , "fabrferreiraecon@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
    Deflate monetary values easily and quickly using the `defvalues` package.
    This package wraps the `deflate()` function from `deflateBR` package, using
    tidyverse's non standard evaluation (NSE) to optimize this task.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports: 
    deflateBR,
    dplyr,
    lubridate,
    rlang
URL: https://github.com/fabrferreira/defvalues
BugReports: https://github.com/fabrferreira/defvalues/issues
